name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Gojo Moonlight Stars Jujutsu Kaisen Gameograf

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Transform your browser with the serene power of Gojo Satoru under a moonlit sky, surrounded by glimmering stars.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Gojo Moonlight Stars Jujutsu Kaisen live wallpaper brings the mystical essence of Jujutsu Kaisen to your Chrome tabs. Watch Gojo bask in the moonlight, a true reflection of his unparalleled strength and enigmatic charm. This extension is perfect for fans who admire his brilliance and want to carry a piece of his world everywhere online.

Key Features
🌌 Gojo-Themed Live Wallpaper: Elegant animations of Gojo under a starry, moonlit sky.
🔍 Google Search Bar: Conduct quick searches without leaving your new tab.
🕒 Clock & Date Widget: Stylishly integrated to help you stay on track.
🌟 Customizable Shortcuts: Add or remove site shortcuts as you like.
⚙️ Extension Controls: Easily manage settings from the bottom left corner.
Embrace the tranquil yet powerful aura of Gojo Satoru and let the moonlit serenity inspire your day with every new tab you open!

For more extensions: https://gameograf.com/
Contact us: https://gameograf.com/contact-us/
Privacy policy: https://gameograf.com/privacy-policy/
